<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.258370>
    dc:description "FIGURES 12 – 18. Adults of Scythropiodes spp. 12, S. elasmatus Park et Wu, ♂; 13, S. oncinius Park et Wu, ♂; 14, S. malivora (Meyrick), ♂; 15 a, S. issikii (Takahashi), ♂; 15 b, S. issikii (Takahashi), ♂; 16, S. triangulus Park et Wu, ♂; 17, S. asymmetricus sp. nov., holotype, ♂; 18, S. taedus sp. nov., paratype, ♂. (Scale bars = 2.0 mm)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/258370/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.258373>
    dc:description "FIGURES 31 – 33. Male genitalia of Scythropiodes spp. 31, S. triangulus Park et Wu, genitalia slide No. WQY 14209; 32, S. asymmetricus sp. nov.: a – c, enlarged distal portion of left valva (a, holotype, genitalia slide No. WQY 13019; b, paratype, genitalia slide No. WQY 15005; c, paratype, genitalia slide No. WQY 14136); 33, S. taedus sp. nov., holotype, genitalia slide No. WQY 13023. (Scale bars = 0.5 mm)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/258373/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.258376>
    dc:description "FIGURES 43 – 44. Female genitalia of Scythropiodes spp. 43, S. asymmetricus sp. nov.: a – c, enlarged signa (a, paratype, genitalia slide No. WQY 14132; b, paratype, genitalia slide No. WQY 14202; c, paratype, genitalia slide No. WQY 14201); 44, S. taedus sp. nov., paratype, genitalia slide No. WQY 15002. (Scale bars = 1.0 mm)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/258376/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

